tabber (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Tabbed terminal sessions using VTE and plink.
  * Sidebar with saved connections and session groups.
  * Quick connect bar for ad-hoc connections.
  * Split panes (horizontal and vertical).
  * Broadcast input mode.
  * Color-coded tabs and connection groups.
  * Auto-reconnect on disconnection.
  * Session logging.
  * Terminal search.
  * SFTP file transfer dialog.
  * Command snippets library.
  * PuTTY session format compatibility.
  * Full keyboard shortcut support.

 -- George Cottrell <georgecottrell@email.com>  Wed, 02 Apr 2026 12:00:00 -0500
